OL,3,CAt the mercy of the weather:
OL,4,CHomeowners lay flooding blame with
OL,5,Cauthorities
OL,7,FITV News Granada Reports journalist
OL,8,FAnna Youssef spent the day with
OL,9,Fresidents who have felt the full
OL,10,Feffects of the floods, while ITV
OL,11,FWeather Presenter Jo Blythe looks
OL,12,Fahead to more weather warnings
OL,14,FResidents and business owners are
OL,15,Fdemanding answers from the authorities
OL,16,Fclaiming they have been left at the
OL,17,Fmercy of the weather following the New
OL,18,FYear flooding.
