OL,7,FThe Environment Agency says that flood
OL,8,Fdefences it has built have defended
OL,9,F21,000 homes in the region, but it
OL,10,Fadmits more work needs to be done.
OL,12,FWith amber warnings for more extreme
OL,13,Fweather on the horizon many are now
OL,14,Ffacing a bleak start to 2025.
OL,16,FFor Julie Lloyd from Abram, Wigan, it
OL,17,Fis a familiar experience. Her home has
OL,18,Fbeen flooded three times since
OL,19,FSeptember, but, she says it does not
OL,20,Fmake it any easier to deal with.
