OL,7,FShe and her husband were both at work
OL,8,Fwhen their security cameras showed
OL,9,Fthat their home was beginning to fill
OL,10,Fwith water in the early hours of New
OL,11,FYear's Day.
OL,13,FThey both rushed home but were
OL,14,Fpowerless to stop the stinking water
OL,15,Fthat filled it to a depth of more than
OL,16,Fa foot, with water from drains and a
OL,17,Fnearby brook taking over the lower
OL,18,Ffloor.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
