OL,7,FRecalling that morning she says: "It
OL,8,Fabsolutely stinks, its awful, its
OL,9,Fabsolutely awful.
OL,11,F"We just couldn't stop it, we tried,
OL,12,Fnext door tried, but we just couldn't
OL,13,Fstop it coming in."
OL,15,FThey had done their best to prepare,
OL,16,Fheeding the flood warnings that were
OL,17,Fissued, but as the ruined carpets and
OL,18,FChristmas decorations show it was not
OL,19,Fenough.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
