OL,7,FShe said New Year's Day should have
OL,8,Fbeen a joyous family gathering, with
OL,9,Fher grandchildren coming to stay
OL,10,Fovernight, but all that remains is the
OL,11,Fstench and shattered hopes.
OL,13,F"It impacts severely really because
OL,14,Fyou lose your electrics, so you can't
OL,15,Fcook, you can't wash," she added.
OL,17,F"We've managed to get some electrics
OL,18,Fon upstairs, so we're running
OL,19,Fextensions.
