OL,7,F"All your appliances downstairs aren't
OL,8,Fworking, its hard to live with really."
OL,10,FNeighbours Stephen and Sheila Christie
OL,11,Fsay they were a little more lucky.
OL,12,FThey 'only' had two inches of water
OL,13,Fenter their home.
OL,15,FThey too had experienced the
OL,16,Fdevastation of flooding at the site
OL,17,Fbefore, and also heeded the warnings
OL,18,Fthis time.
OL,20,FBut like Julie they couldn't stem the
OL,21,Frising tide of sewage and rain water.
