OL,7,FHe says he feels all the bodies
OL,8,Finvolved in managing the problem need
OL,9,Fto come together to coordinate their
OL,10,Fefforts to manage water more
OL,11,Feffectively, and that its an issue
OL,12,Fthat needs addressing not just across
OL,13,Fthe North West, but across the country
OL,14,Fas a whole.
OL,16,FResidents feel that no-one is taking
OL,17,Fresponsibility for the repeated
OL,18,Fflooding at the site, and that they
OL,19,Fare being left to fend for themselves.
