OL,7,FIn a statement Wigan Council said:
OL,8,F"Wigan Council works in partnership
OL,9,Fwith a number of organisations to
OL,10,Fmanage flood risk and help communities
OL,11,Fto become more resilient to flooding.
OL,13,F"We deeply empathise with residents
OL,14,Faffected by the recent flooding over
OL,15,Fthe New Year period, caused by
OL,16,Fsignificant rainfall over a short
OL,17,Fperiod.
