OL,7,F"Wigan Borough has its own Local Flood
OL,8,FRisk Management Strategy and our teams
OL,9,Fregularly review our approaches to
OL,10,Fmitigate the impact of flooding.
OL,12,F"Wherever possible, we offer a range
OL,13,Fof support to those affected and our
OL,14,Fofficers have been supporting
OL,15,Fresidents throughout these recent
OL,16,Fincidents. We will continue to work
OL,17,Fclosely with agencies as it is
OL,18,Fimportant to note that no single
OL,19,Forganisation can eliminate all flood
OL,20,Frisks."
