OL,7,FA United Utilities spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"The recent flooding in Bickershaw
OL,9,FLane was caused when nearby Hey Brook
OL,10,Fbroke its bank and water levels rose
OL,11,Fdramatically.
OL,13,F"We understand the frustration of
OL,14,Fresidents living in the area so, after
OL,15,Fan earlier flooding incident, we
OL,16,Fcarried out work to increase capacity
OL,17,Fin the brook by removing debris that
OL,18,Fhad been dumped in the short section
OL,19,Fthat is in our ownership.
